data.description: Welcome to this versatile 11.904 acre property w/ a 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch style home located inside Montgomery city limits MINUTES from downtown Montgomery w/ easy access to The Woodlands, Houston and College Station! 5 of the 11.894 acres are ag exempt and are suitable for cattle, horses, or farming. The entire property is fenced and cross fenced w/ a huge 40x30 outdoor insulated workshop/barn w/ a wood stove, large equipment shed, multiple loafing sheds w/ corrals, hay barn w/ a tack and feed room, cattle chute and a well. Enjoy fishing on the massive stocked pond, a perfect place to enjoy your morning coffee by. Inside, the kitchen features new stainless steel appliances, upgraded granite counter tops w/ cabinets GALORE, new tile backsplash and overlooks the spacious living room with vaulted ceilings and a wood burning stove for those cool Texas evenings. Sellers have installed new carpet, fresh paint throughout and updated light fixtures. Low taxes, Montgomery schools, and No HOA
